    <h2 style="color: #1e40af; font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
      <span>₿</span>
      <span>加密货币分析</span>
      <span style="font-size: 0.8rem; background: #FFD700; color: #fff; padding: 0.2rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: bold;">热门</span>
    </h2>
    <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0;">
      <li style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
        <a href="/crypto/btc" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;">₿ Bitcoin (BTC) 分析 →</a>
      </li>
      <li style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
        <a href="/crypto/eth" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;">♦ Ethereum (ETH) 分析 →</a>
      </li>
      <li style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
        <a href="/crypto/sol" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;">◎ Solana (SOL) 分析 →</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- 足球比赛预测板块 -->
