    </h2>
    <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 0.5rem;">
      <li style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
        <a href="https://869.us.ci/stock-analysis/aapl-20260331/" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;">🍎 Apple (AAPL) 分析 →</a>
      </li>
      <li style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
        <a href="https://869.us.ci/stock-analysis/tsla-20260331/" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;">🚗 Tesla (TSLA) 分析 →</a>
      </li>
      <li style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
        <a href="https://869.us.ci/stock-analysis/nvda-20260331/" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;">🎮 Nvidia (NVDA) 分析 →</a>
      </li>
      <li style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
        <a href="https://869.us.ci/stock-analysis/msft-20260331/" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;">💻 Microsoft (MSFT) 分析 →</a>
      </li>
      <li style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
