      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- 为什么选择我们板块 -->
  <section style="margin-top: 2rem; padding: 2rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFD700 0%, #FFA500 100%); border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.4); position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
    <!-- 装饰性金币图案 -->
    <div style="position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 10px; font-size: 3rem; opacity: 0.2;">💰</div>
    <div style="position: absolute; bottom: 10px; left: 10px; font-size: 3rem; opacity: 0.2;">💎</div>
    
    <h3 style="color: #fff; font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: center; text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); position: relative; z-index: 1;">
      ✨ 为什么选择我们？
    </h3>
    <ul style="line-height: 2.2; color: #fff; font-size: 1.1rem; position: relative; z-index: 1;">
      <li>✅ <strong>实时数据采集</strong> - 每 4 小时自动更新市场行情</li>
      <li>✅ <strong>AI 智能分析</strong> - DeepSeek AI 驱动的专业预测</li>
      <li>✅ <strong>SEO 优化</strong> - Google 友好的结构化数据</li>
      <li>✅ <strong>完全免费</strong> - 无广告干扰的纯净内容</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  
  <!-- 底部黄金分隔线 -->
  <div style="height: 4px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #FFD700, transparent); margin: 2rem 0 1rem; border-radius: 2px;"></div>
  
  <!-- CSS 动画定义 -->
  <style>
    @keyframes shine {
      0% { transform: translateX(-100%) rotate(45deg); }
      100% { transform: translateX(100%) rotate(45deg); }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
